-- ds.page-with-toc: Why Not?
sub-sections: $config.web-product-header
toc: $config.product-manual-toc

As much as we like our product, a why not section should be there to
identify why not to use our product. Things that we do not want to
support, things where we believe people may be doing suboptimal choices
by choosing to use us etc should be documented here.
